# Cursor Rules - Project Organization

This directory contains organized rules and guidelines for different types of projects.

## Directory Structure

```
.cursor/rules/
├── general/              # Universal rules applicable to all projects
├── llm-ai/              # LLM/AI system development (PocketFlow)
├── workflow-automation/ # n8n, ActivePieces workflow automation
